{
  "stem": "10397.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, sure, tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A Ukrainian fellow, nice guy, nice guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we load-- I loaded a sack of food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I go with him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and he gave me such a coat, which they use when there is a storm, with a-- with a-- with a caboose, you know, a cover, and all the way.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When it's 30 below 0, you know, and you have to go working in the woods, that's what you wear there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I walked into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I-- I visited with my mother and my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I brought a-- on-- on my shoulders.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He-- he had to stay outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He had a wagon and horses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I took the-- the sack of food and carry it and walk into this apartment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The first time I walked in, I thought I'll pass out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "One room, the grass grows from the-- between the boards of the-- of the-- of the floor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My mother is fading.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My father is very sick, not bedridden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But she cooked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My father was depressed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I come out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I talk to this millwright.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to walk a little.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I says, I don't know what to do with my parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He says, I can save one, mother or father, but I can't take both of them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SOB] So I go back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I tell them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, my father tells my mother, you go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So no, you go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she says, you go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, I can't sit here forever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I got to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, I took my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Father didn't want to go, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I managed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I brought the food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I say, I bring you food, again, again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because you know, he says, anytime you need me, food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He wasn't hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "People are dying from hunger, because they're sending people on the-- by the fence.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If you have a gold watch, a ring, sometimes they give you food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But how many people have gold watches or gold rings or gold earrings or money or whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Eventually, everybody runs out of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You have no money, you have to die from starvation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because the only productive part of the society is the farmer in such a situation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Anyway, I took out my mother from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And put her-- we-- we traveling on this wagon-- in this wagon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I come to their house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I kiss my mother on top-- [CRYING] [SOBBING] And he says, OK.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We're all right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You-- we'll feed you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I go back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I'll be here tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She is there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she's depressed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[SOB] Three days later-- four days later, the farmer comes into the-- to my-- to my office says, she wants to go back [SOBBING] to the ghetto, stay with your father.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She wants to die with your father, she says.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [SOBBING] I go there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SOB] We had a big session.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SOBBING] The farmer was crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CRYING] The father-- farmer was crying, everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SOB] Took her back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never saw her again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SOBBING] 20th of May, liquidated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Took them to the woods, everyone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's their technique.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the-- the Ukrainian police helped them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Polish fire department helped them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Polish fire-- firemen carry a-- a hatchet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, if they go to a-- a-- a small hatchet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know what is a hatchet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They go to, when there's a fire, to break up, when something is in the way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, to take care of the fire, they break up, with the hatchet, the wooden structures.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if that-- the Jews didn't want to go, they break their feet with the-- with the hatchet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's the Polish-- Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And Ukrainians had guns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was the militsiya, the police, with the guns, with everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's the-- the end of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the 20th of May, that was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
